{"tid":1352902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來何君堯個議員就職宣誓 都有問題 可被DQ","createTime":"2019-07-23T00:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T00:48:59.000Z","uid":28257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8971319ec031979257a5b4ac858cd1c855e0b87e","tid":1352902,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:47:24.000Z","msg":"原來二零一六年十月十二號，何君堯宣誓時，<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UcGignv3Vpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUcGignv3Vpg&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=01c48dc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UcGignv3Vpg</a>自己睇片48:49)<br />\n<br />\n將誓詞宣讀成中KOWK..中華人民共和國 (議員因為宣誓時間，咬字清晰度，與誓詞的增添省刪等，構成宣誓無效。)，並宣稱自己會遵守法律，廉潔奉公 - WOW。我地可以捉實呢樣野。二來加上佢身為議員，竟然前晚同班元朗黑道人仕握手言歡，<span style=\"color: red;\">實在唔合適繼續出任議員</span>。入稟法院將佢DQ， 加埋民陣搞遊行同集會，泛民再加持一下，要高等法院/終審法院(<span style=\"color: red;\">將司法權，法律界拉埋入黎，以一權對二權</span>) 要審視何君堯的議員資格 (當時梁遊宣誓風波，高等法院一個月就有判決。) 。<br />\n<br />\n宜家警黑合作，濫權用暴，證據確鑿，市民受累。現今市民已無所依，唯有訴諸司法權。社會處於動盪邊緣。市民各界對警隊完完全全失去信心，認為佢地無能力維持治安。政府一係政府解散警隊，由消防暫任其公職，或者法庭審視現時警隊的合法性，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求每個警員重新宣誓，以保護市民的人身及財產之安全為首要職務，以非效宗國家/政府同上司命令為首</span>。"},{"pid":"06268b768f8bc5bb1a8c8b44bd5cc124ba38a480","tid":1352902,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}